text: Chuyunchi-Nikolayevka () is a rural locality (a selo) in Chuyunchinsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 558 as of 2010. There are 7 streets. == Geography == It is located 40 km from Davlekanovo, 3 km from Chuyunchi. == References == Category:Rural localities in Davlekanovsky District
title: Chuyunchi-Nikolayevka
